<style 
      xmlns="http://purl.org/net/xbiblio/csl"
      class="note"
      version="1.0" page-range-format="chicago">
  <info>
    <id />
    <title />
    <updated>2009-08-10T04:49:00+09:00</updated>
  </info>
  <citation>
    <layout delimiter="; ">
      <group delimiter=" ">
        <text variable="page"/>
        <choose>
          <if is-numeric="page">
            <text value="(is-numeric)"/>
          </if>
          <else>
            <text value="(non-numeric)"/>
          </else>
        </choose>
      </group>
    </layout>
  </citation>
</style>
